I"Å&<ul>
  <li>(please refer to my previous post:  <a href="http://rolandtanglao.com/2020/10/20/p1-barcode-ggplot2-kludge/">R and ggplot2 pseudo code for barcode of Firefox questions</a>)</li>
  <li>Here‚Äôs the actual code from <a href="https://github.com/rtanglao/rt-r-ggplot2-ruby-experiments/blob/main/simplest-possible-ff-question-barcode.R">simplest-possible-ff-question-barcode.R</a> with a kludgy <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">for</code> loop (I think it will be better without a <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">for</code> loop, but that will have to wait for the next post :-) !):</li>
</ul>

